      "content": "yeah i think it's just the food. i was sitting weird on the couch so maybe my arm is just tense from that too. it doesn't feel like an emergency or anything, just really uncomfortable. you're pretty sure it's just indigestion right? i'd rather not sit in an ER waiting room all night for nothing if it's just heartburn.",
